		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Tue, Feb 22nd 10:07 AM2005 </span><span class="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a class="sm" href="/db/classes.html?class=4&mid=1109003092701726934&num=1&page=0&post=1&replyto=1109084831435898903"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a></a>    <a name=1109084831435898903></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform2" ><span class="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=247125"><span id="Scholar">Jiggidyjay of the Seven Seas</span></a><b><span id="Scholar"><br>Scholar</span></b><br /><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*" /><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*"/><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*" /><br />1935 posts
		   <br /><nobr><span class="notbold">Score</span>: Good [3.56]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Jiggidyjay&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%">
<p>Psalm of mystic shielding will probably be more useful in most situations. Just remember that the absorb damage component is kind of like a rune, so if you're tank is getting nuked a lot, the song is going to keep dropping. <br /> <br />Another thing to look at is the DS from your other psalms. It's not huge, but it is modded by voice, so if you wanted to amp it once in a while, it could be nice, especially since slowing at that level really isn't that effective. <br /> <br />So, if you want the extra HP regen and MR, go with shielding. If you want a specific resist and a stacking DS, go with one of the elemental/disease/poison psalms. It's going to depend on your group and situation more then anything.</p>
